# Project Rules
## Git
- Only commit and push to main when explicitly asked by the user
- Never auto-commit or auto-push after making changes
- Never create new branches — always use main
- Use clear descriptive commit messages
## Server
- Always make file changes directly without waiting for background processes
- After making file changes, restart the local server automatically
## Project Info
- This is a plain HTML/CSS website for Rocker Industries
- Pages: index.html, about.html, solutions.html, applications.html, quality.html, contact.html
- Images are stored in the /images folder
## General
- Never create new files unless explicitly asked
- Always confirm when changes are complete
